# Stream Health Monitor: Project Overview

**Goal:** Create a centralized dashboard for real-time monitoring of live video stream health from various sources, comparing it against local network/hardware capabilities.

**Core Problem:** Lack of unified visibility into stream health and performance potential.

**Target Users:** Broadcast engineers and managers needing quick confirmation of broadcast quality.

